commit e61a0e3f15ac0dec934f7ef77a61d0a3ab47d52f
Author: Pieter Noordhuis <pcnoordhuis@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Oct 24 10:45:43 2018 -0700

    Add new style allreduce collective (#143)

    Summary:
    This implements a ring reduction resulting the result scattered across
    processes, followed by an allgather operation to the root process.

    It can take multiple inputs and multiple outputs. If the inputs are not
    specified it is assumed to be an in place operation on the outputs.
    Pull Request resolved: https://github.com/facebookincubator/gloo/pull/143

    Reviewed By: manojkris

    Differential Revision: D10376434

    Pulled By: pietern

    fbshipit-source-id: 17a6ab7e02591a351e551c8582f0095041ddcf05
