commit cba46a4869b3e95777d0b50953a409824ad448f0
Author: Pieter Noordhuis <pietern@fb.com>
Date:   Thu May 18 14:23:43 2017 -0700

    Assert that we don't do out of bound writes on recv

    Summary:
    The halving/doubling algorithm had two instances where a receive
    buffer was registered with a number of elements instead of a number of
